{"tid":2031352,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨單日令恆指損失1. 7萬億","createTime":"2020-05-23T10:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T18:20:59.000Z","uid":338879,"like":283,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"640e8cd6751664443bf4cc336560111a23667bd6","tid":2031352,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"共產黨一條法，搞到恆指冇左1.7萬億<br />\n<br />\n以700萬人計，每人冇左24. 2萬<br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝黨，我愛黨</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「港版國安法」納入全國人大會議議程，引起市場憂慮，港股周五被嚇散，恒指急挫1349點（5.56%），跌幅為2015年7月以來最勁，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">單日蒸發市值近1.7萬億元</span></strong>；主板成交按日大增四成半至1805億元，是兩個幾月以來最多。俗稱「港股恐慌指數」的恒指波幅指數（VHSI）飆四成至35.28；主板沽空比率攀至17.11%，為3周之最。藍籌股全線下跌，多達33隻股份跌幅超過半成。不過，「北水」毋懼本港政治局勢，「港股通」連續9個交易日淨買入，周五單日再錄得44億元資金流入。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2473479/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E9%99%B7%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C+%E6%8F%921349%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2473479%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2582%25A1%25E9%2599%25B7%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2585%258C%2B%25E6%258F%25921349%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2582%25B7&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=c33fec01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2473479/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E9%99%B7%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C+%E6%8F%921349%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"a012dced734327613fd762e3b97d405ff8855d72","tid":2031352,"uid":338879,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"640e8cd6751664443bf4cc336560111a23667bd6","tid":2031352,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"共產黨一條法，搞到恆指冇左1.7萬億<br />\n<br />\n以700萬人計，每人冇左24. 2萬<br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝黨，我愛黨</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<b